{"title":"战士红心向太阳","authors":["姜桂祥"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":9,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士红心向太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军战士　姜桂祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝书怀中揣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士眼睛亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢枪握在手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀闪银光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切为革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哨位是战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛勤送黑夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑脸迎曙光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕暴风雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戴雪又披霜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身是力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗决心大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命志如钢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身挑千斤担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢向前闯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"言行全一致，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心永向党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山也敢上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不忘阶级苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血谱新章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提高警惕性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚守哨位上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切为人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心永远向太阳。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}